《'''卡巴里'''》（Kabali）是2016年[[泰米尔语|泰米尔语]]的印度[[黑幫電影|黑幫電影]]，由{{le|Pa. Ranjith|Pa. Ranjith}}編劇及導演，製片是{{le|S. Thanu|S. Thanu}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/kabali-the-album-of-rajinikanths-film-will-be-launched-on-june-11/1/683230.html|title=Kabali: Music album of Rajinikanths gangster film to be launched on June 11|publisher=|accessdate=18 June 2016|archive-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815062836/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/kabali-the-album-of-rajinikanths-film-will-be-launched-on-june-11/1/683230.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。劇情以卡巴里（Kabaleeswaran，由{{le|Rajinikanth|Rajinikanth}}飾演）及Tony Lee（由[[趙文瑄|趙文瑄]]飾演）之間的幫派鬥爭為主。主演的還有由[[拉德西卡·阿普泰|拉德西卡·阿普泰]]、{{le|Dhansika|Dhansika}}、{{le|Dinesh Ravi|Dinesh Ravi}}、{{le|Kalaiyarasan|Kalaiyarasan}}及{{le|John Vijay|John Vijay}}等人。

